Module nl.naturalis.common

Package nl.naturalis.common.time

Date/time utility classes.
  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    FuzzyDate
    A FuzzyDate represents the result of parsing a date string into a date/time object.
    FuzzyDateParser
    Parses date strings into FuzzyDate instances.
    ParseInfo
    A ParseInfo specifies how to parse a date string.
    YearFilter
    A DateStringFilter implementation used as a very course, last ditch attempt to at least extract a year from date strings like "2007b" or "1914 - 1918".
  • Exception Summary
    Exception Description
    FuzzyDateException
    Thrown if an error occurs while parsing a date string or if no year could be extract from the date string.
